<h1>EventosOmega - Documento de Contexto Tecnico</h1>
<p class="meta">Versao: maio/2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Stack: Next.js 16.2.6, React 19, Prisma 5.22, PostgreSQL, NextAuth v5, Mercado Pago</p>

<h2>1. Visao Geral do Sistema</h2>

<h3>1.1 Objetivo principal</h3>
<p><strong>EventosOmega</strong> e uma plataforma de venda e gestao de ingressos para eventos, inspirada no modelo Sympla. O sistema permite:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Descoberta publica</strong> de eventos (home, busca, categorias, paginas por slug)</li>
  <li><strong>Inscricao dinamica</strong> com formularios configuraveis por evento (<code>Event.formStructure</code>)</li>
  <li><strong>Pagamento</strong> via Mercado Pago com split de taxa Moove (2%)</li>
  <li><strong>Gestao operacional</strong> por organizadores (<code>/dashboard/*</code>) e administradores (<code>/admin/*</code>)</li>
  <li><strong>Patrocinios na home</strong>: carrossel de logos (<code>PlatformSponsor</code>) e banner promocional (<code>PlatformBannerMedia</code>)</li>
</ul>

<h3>1.2 Arquitetura geral</h3>
<p><strong>Monolito full-stack</strong> com Next.js App Router:</p>
<table>
  <tr><th>Camada</th><th>Tecnologia</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Frontend + Backend</td><td>Next.js 16 (App Router, Server Components + Client Components)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>API</td><td>Route Handlers em <code>src/app/api/**/route.ts</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>ORM / DB</td><td>Prisma 5 + PostgreSQL</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Auth</td><td>NextAuth v5 (Auth.js beta) - JWT + Credentials</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pagamentos</td><td>Mercado Pago SDK v2 (Preferences + Webhooks)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>UI</td><td>Tailwind CSS 3 + Radix UI + componentes estilo Shadcn</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Tudo roda no mesmo processo Next.js (<code>next dev</code> / <code>next start</code>). Nao ha microsservicos.</p>

<h3>1.3 Stack tecnologica</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Categoria</th><th>Tecnologias</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Linguagem</td><td>TypeScript 5 (strict)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Framework</td><td>Next.js ^16.2.6, React ^19</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Banco</td><td>PostgreSQL via Prisma ^5.22.0</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Auth</td><td>next-auth ^5.0.0-beta.25, bcryptjs</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Validacao</td><td>Zod ^3.24.1, @hookform/resolvers</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pagamentos</td><td>mercadopago ^2.0.15</td></tr>
  <tr><td>UI</td><td>Radix UI, lucide-react, framer-motion, tailwindcss-animate</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Datas</td><td>date-fns</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Forms</td><td>react-hook-form</td></tr>
</table>
<p><strong>Scripts npm:</strong> <code>dev</code> (prisma generate + next dev), <code>postinstall</code> (prisma generate), <code>db:push</code>, <code>db:migrate</code>, <code>db:seed</code>, <code>db:studio</code></p>
<p><strong>Limites de upload</strong> (<code>next.config.ts</code>): middlewareClientMaxBodySize e serverActions bodySizeLimit = 20mb</p>

<h2>2. Estrutura de Pastas e Organizacao</h2>

<pre>EventosOmega/
├── prisma/
│   ├── schema.prisma          # Modelos, enums, relacoes
│   └── seed.ts                # Admin, organizador demo, eventos
├── public/                    # Assets estaticos
├── src/
│   ├── app/                   # App Router - paginas e API routes
│   │   ├── layout.tsx         # Layout raiz: Navbar, SessionProvider
│   │   ├── page.tsx           # Home publica
│   │   ├── middleware.ts      # Guard de roles (Edge)
│   │   ├── admin/             # Area ADMIN (sidebar propria)
│   │   ├── dashboard/         # Area ORGANIZER/ADMIN
│   │   ├── event/[slug]/      # Pagina publica canonica
│   │   ├── checkout/[id]/     # Retry de pagamento
│   │   ├── payment/           # Landing success/failure MP
│   │   └── api/               # Route Handlers REST
│   ├── auth.ts                # NextAuth Node.js
│   ├── auth.config.ts         # NextAuth Edge-safe
│   ├── components/            # UI por dominio
│   ├── hooks/                 # use-transaction, use-toast
│   ├── lib/                   # Logica compartilhada server-side
│   └── types/                 # Tipos TS + extensao NextAuth
├── next.config.ts
└── tsconfig.json              # Alias @/* → ./src/*</pre>

<table>
  <tr><th>Diretorio</th><th>Proposito</th></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/app/</code></td><td>Rotas, layouts e API. page.tsx e Server Component por padrao</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/app/api/</code></td><td>Backend HTTP: enroll, checkout, webhooks, CRUD admin</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/components/admin/</code></td><td>AdminEventForm, ParticipantTable, PlatformSponsorManager, PlatformBannerManager</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/components/events/</code></td><td>DynamicEventForm, EventCard, EventCoverImage</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/components/home/</code></td><td>HeroCarousel, CategoryNav, HomeOrganizerBanner, HomeSponsorLogoCarousel</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>src/lib/</code></td><td>fee.ts, mercadopago.ts, prisma.ts, validations.ts, sponsor-media.ts</td></tr>
  <tr><td><code>prisma/</code></td><td>Schema e seed - fonte da verdade do dominio</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>3. Fluxo de Dados e Funcionalidades Principais</h2>

<h3>3.1 Modelo de dominio (Prisma)</h3>
<pre>User ──1:N──► Event (organizerId)
User ──1:N──► Participant
Event ──1:N──► TicketType
Event ──1:N──► Participant
Event ──1:N──► EventSponsorMedia (legado)
TicketType ──1:N──► Participant
Participant ──1:1──► Transaction
PlatformSponsor (global)
PlatformBannerMedia (global)</pre>

<p><strong>Enums criticos:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><code>UserRole</code>: ADMIN | ORGANIZER | BUYER</li>
  <li><code>EventStatus</code>: DRAFT | PUBLISHED | CANCELLED | FINISHED</li>
  <li><code>ParticipantStatus</code>: REGISTERED → CONFIRMED → CHECKED_IN | CANCELLED | REFUNDED</li>
  <li><code>TransactionStatus</code>: PENDING → APPROVED | REJECTED | CANCELLED | REFUNDED | ...</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Campos JSON dinamicos:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><code>Event.formStructure</code>: { fields: FormField[] } - campos extras de inscricao</li>
  <li><code>Participant.formData</code>: respostas do participante</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Identificador humano:</strong> <code>Participant.ordemCompra</code> - autoincrement global para check-in/suporte.</p>

<h3>3.2 Regra financeira Moove (critica)</h3>
<p>Implementada exclusivamente em <code>src/lib/fee.ts</code>:</p>
<pre>calculateMooveFee(grossAmount: number): FeeCalculation
// mooveFee = 2% do grossValue (calculo em centavos)
// organizerAmount = grossValue - mooveFee</pre>
<p>Usada em: <code>POST /api/enroll</code>, <code>POST /api/checkout</code>, <code>POST /api/webhooks/mercadopago</code>.</p>
<p><strong>O cliente nunca envia valores monetarios.</strong></p>

<h3>3.3 Fluxo de autenticacao</h3>
<pre>LoginForm → signIn("credentials")
  → auth.ts authorize() → bcrypt.compare + prisma.user.findUnique
  → JWT com id, role, mercadoPagoUserId
  → middleware.ts (auth.config authorized callback)</pre>

<table>
  <tr><th>Rota</th><th>Roles permitidos</th></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/login</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/*</td><td>ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/dashboard/*</td><td>ADMIN | ORGANIZER</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Demais rotas</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Helpers API</strong> (<code>src/lib/event-auth.ts</code>):</p>
<ul>
  <li><code>requireAdmin()</code> - definido, nao utilizado</li>
  <li><code>requireEventManager()</code> - ADMIN ou ORGANIZER</li>
  <li><code>canManageEvent(session, eventId)</code> - ADMIN passa; ORGANIZER so se event.organizerId === session.user.id</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Credenciais seed</strong> (<code>prisma/seed.ts</code>):</p>
<ul>
  <li>Admin: admin@eventosomega.com / Admin@2026!</li>
  <li>Organizador: organizer@eventosomega.com / Org@2026!</li>
</ul>

<h3>3.4 Fluxo de inscricao e pagamento</h3>
<pre>DynamicEventForm (client)
  → POST /api/enroll
      ├── Valida enrollSchema (Zod)
      ├── Valida campos obrigatorios de formStructure
      ├── Verifica estoque (totalQuantity - soldQuantity)
      ├── upsert User (role BUYER)
      ├── prisma.$transaction: Participant + Transaction + soldQuantity++
      ├── Se price = 0 → CONFIRMED + APPROVED (sem MP)
      └── Se pago → fetch interno POST /api/checkout → redirectTo (initPoint MP)

Mercado Pago → POST /api/webhooks/mercadopago
  ├── verifyMpSignature() - HMAC-SHA256 + timingSafeEqual
  ├── getPaymentClient().get() - status real no MP
  ├── Reconcilia transaction_amount vs grossValue
  └── APPROVED → Participant CONFIRMED
      REJECTED/CANCELLED → libera estoque (soldQuantity--)</pre>

<p><strong>Componentes pos-pagamento:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><code>/payment/success</code> - landing MP</li>
  <li><code>/checkout/[id]</code> + <code>RetryPaymentButton</code> - nova tentativa</li>
  <li><code>useTransaction()</code> - polling em GET /api/participants/[id]/transaction</li>
</ul>

<h3>3.5 Fluxo de criacao/gestao de eventos</h3>
<pre>AdminEventForm / CreateEventForm
  → POST /api/admin/events (requireEventManager)
      ├── adminEventSchema (Zod) - formStructure + ticketTypes
      ├── generateSlug() + uniqueSlug()
      └── organizerId = session.user.id

Dashboard (/dashboard)
  → prisma.event.findMany({ where: { organizerId: session.user.id } })

Edicao
  → PATCH /api/admin/events/[id] (requireEventManager + canManageEvent)</pre>

<h3>3.6 Fluxo da home publica (src/app/page.tsx)</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Funcao</th><th>Fonte</th><th>Componente UI</th></tr>
  <tr><td>getHeroSlides()</td><td>Event publicados</td><td>HeroCarousel</td></tr>
  <tr><td>getPlatformSponsorLogos()</td><td>PlatformSponsor ativos</td><td>HomeSponsorLogoCarousel</td></tr>
  <tr><td>getEvents(q, city)</td><td>Event + filtros</td><td>EventCard grid</td></tr>
  <tr><td>getSponsorPromoSlides()</td><td>PlatformBannerMedia ativos</td><td>HomeOrganizerBanner</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Query params: <code>?q=</code> (busca), <code>?city=</code> (filtro por cidade).</p>

<h3>3.7 Fluxo de patrocinadores</h3>
<p>Gerenciado em <strong>/dashboard/sponsors</strong> (ORGANIZER + ADMIN):</p>
<table>
  <tr><th>Componente</th><th>Model</th><th>API</th></tr>
  <tr><td>PlatformSponsorManager</td><td>PlatformSponsor</td><td>/api/admin/platform-sponsors</td></tr>
  <tr><td>PlatformBannerManager</td><td>PlatformBannerMedia</td><td>/api/admin/platform-banners</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Exibicao publica: GET /api/promo/platform-sponsors (logos), GET /api/promo/sponsors (banner, slide 3s).</p>
<p>Limites em <code>src/lib/sponsor-media.ts</code>: banner 42:9, imagem 10MB, video 8MB/5s; logo 2MB.</p>

<h2>4. Integracoes e APIs</h2>

<h3>4.1 Mercado Pago</h3>
<p><strong>Arquivo:</strong> <code>src/lib/mercadopago.ts</code></p>
<table>
  <tr><th>Export</th><th>Uso</th></tr>
  <tr><td>getPreferenceClient()</td><td>Criacao de checkout (POST /api/checkout)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>getPaymentClient()</td><td>Consulta de pagamento no webhook</td></tr>
  <tr><td>buildIdempotencyKey(prefix, stableId)</td><td>Chaves unicas por tentativa</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Variaveis de ambiente:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><code>MERCADOPAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN</code> - obrigatorio para pagamentos</li>
  <li><code>MERCADOPAGO_WEBHOOK_SECRET</code> - validacao HMAC (obrigatorio em producao)</li>
  <li><code>NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL</code> - back_urls e fetch interno enroll→checkout</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Preference</strong> (checkout/route.ts): marketplace_fee = mooveFee (2%), external_reference = participantId, expiracao 30 min.</p>
<p><strong>Webhook</strong> (webhooks/mercadopago/route.ts): verifyMpSignature(), idempotencia por mercadoPagoPaymentId, reconciliacao de valor.</p>

<h3>4.2 NextAuth (Auth.js v5)</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Arquivo</th><th>Runtime</th><th>Responsabilidade</th></tr>
  <tr><td>auth.config.ts</td><td>Edge</td><td>authorized, JWT/session callbacks</td></tr>
  <tr><td>auth.ts</td><td>Node.js</td><td>Credentials provider + Prisma + bcrypt</td></tr>
  <tr><td>api/auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts</td><td>Node.js</td><td>Export handlers</td></tr>
</table>
<p>Secret usado: <code>AUTH_SECRET</code> (nao NEXTAUTH_SECRET do .env.example).</p>

<h3>4.3 Mapa de paginas (App Router)</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Rota</th><th>Arquivo</th><th>Acesso</th></tr>
  <tr><td>/</td><td>app/page.tsx</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/event/[slug]</td><td>app/event/[slug]/page.tsx</td><td>Publico (canonico)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/events/[id]</td><td>app/events/[id]/page.tsx</td><td>Redirect 308 → slug</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/checkout/[id]</td><td>app/checkout/[id]/page.tsx</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/payment/success|failure</td><td>app/payment/*/page.tsx</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/login</td><td>app/admin/login/page.tsx</td><td>Publico</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin</td><td>app/admin/page.tsx</td><td>ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/dashboard</td><td>app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx</td><td>ADMIN (KPIs financeiros)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/events/*</td><td>app/admin/events/**</td><td>ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/admin/sponsors</td><td>Redirect → /dashboard/sponsors</td><td>ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/dashboard</td><td>app/dashboard/page.tsx</td><td>ORGANIZER/ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/dashboard/events/*</td><td>CRUD eventos do organizador</td><td>ORGANIZER/ADMIN</td></tr>
  <tr><td>/dashboard/sponsors</td><td>Patrocinadores + banner</td><td>ORGANIZER/ADMIN</td></tr>
</table>

